g><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1ex6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Kutta/">Kutta</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 January 2010 08:14:26PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1ex6'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1ex6'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1ex6')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1ex6" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
